## Key Improvements

### 1. Unified Dark Theme
- Replaced jarring light/dark split with cohesive `#0f172a` dark background
- All panels now use consistent `--bg-secondary` (#1e293b) color

### 2. Vibrant Node Colors
- Start: Blue glow (`#3b82f6`)
- LLM: Emerald glow (`#10b981`)
- Tool: Amber glow (`#f59e0b`)
- Router: Purple glow (`#8b5cf6`)
- Reducer: Pink glow (`#ec4899`)
- LoopGuard: Cyan glow (`#06b6d4`)
- End: Red glow (`#ef4444`)

### 3. Glassmorphism Effects
- Toolbar uses `backdrop-filter: blur(12px)` with semi-transparent background
- Step controls and overlays have frosted glass appearance

### 4. Improved Typography
- Imported Inter font from Google Fonts
- Gradient text on titles for premium feel
- Better font weights and spacing

### 5. Micro-Animations
- Hover effects with `transform: translateY(-2px)` on cards
- Icon scaling on button hover
- Smooth transitions with custom timing variables

